ons to the Gervais-Neveu-Felder equation and identities for the\nFelder's elliptic $R$-matrix are also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 27 Nov 2015 17:51:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 6 Dec 2015 16:55:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 18 May 2016 20:54:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-22"}
